                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9599" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1442</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1579 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">恒瑞医药：投融资战略赋能企业科技创新</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hengrui Pharmaceutical: Investment and financing strategy enables enterprise scientific and technological innovation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘李福，孟禹衡，周丽苹，胡婕，许多，王文萍</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南财经大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏恒瑞医药股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">投融资战略；科技创新；恒瑞医药</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Investment and financing strategy; Scientific and technological innovation; Hengrui Pharmaceutical</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在全球医药产业加速创新的背景下，科技创新正成为企业价值提升的核心驱动力。作为我国制药行业科技创新的典型代表，恒瑞医药于2020年成功入选全球医药发明指数和医药创新指数排行榜，成为我国唯一获此殊荣的制药企业。这一成就得益于恒瑞医药长期以来对科技创新的坚定承诺和实践投入，同时也离不开其独特的投融资战略，为企业的科技创新提供了坚实的财务后盾。本案例着重分析恒瑞医药如何通过内源融资、剥离非核心业务、引进创新人才和研发投入等投融资战略赋能科技创新，以此实现企业价值的显著提升。基于案例实践，学员可以系统掌握投融资战略如何优化资源配置、提升创新效率，从而拓宽学员对公司投融资、经营和治理等行为的理解，为将来在实际工作中制定和执行有效的财务战略，储备理论知识和实践参考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In the context of accelerating innovation in the global pharmaceutical industry, technological innovation is becoming the core driver of enterprise value. As a typical representative of technological innovation in China&#39;s pharmaceutical industry, Hengrui Pharmaceuticals successfully made it onto the global pharmaceutical patent index and innovation index ranking list in 2020, becoming the only pharmaceutical enterprise in China to receive this honor. This achievement is the result of Hengrui Pharmaceuticals&#39; long-term commitment and practical investment in technological innovation, and it would not have been possible without its unique investment and financing strategy, which provides a solid financial backing for the company&#39;s technological innovation. This case focuses on how Hengrui Pharmaceuticals has empowered technological innovation through internal financing, divesting non-core businesses, attracting innovative talent, and investing in research and development, thereby achieving significant enhancement of enterprise value. Based on the practical case, learners can systematically master how investment and financing strategies optimize resource allocation and enhance innovation efficiency, thereby broadening their understanding of the company&#39;s investment and financing, operation, and governance behaviors, and preparing theoretical knowledge and practical references for formulating and implementing effective financial strategies in future work.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">创新理论；优序融资理论；微笑曲线理论；组织变革理论；内部控制理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-05</td>
                            </tr>
